cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG 

The paper proposes a MultiModal quality recognition approach for the quality score, which involves using feature extractors for both image and text and an Siamese Network with the rank loss as the optimization objective. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the following arXiv CS sub-categories: 

- cs.MM (Multimedia)
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval)
- cs.CV (Computer Vision)
- cs.CL (Computation and Language)
- cs.LG (Machine Learning)
